text: Bulazh () is a rural locality (a village) in Sterlibashevsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 62 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Sterlibashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Bulazh
